"""
Write a Python script that prompts the user to input two numbers.
Calculate the average of these two numbers and print the result.
This task aims to evaluate your ability to interact with users through
input statements and perform basic arithmetic operations in Python.
"""

number1 = int(input("Insert first number: "))
number2 = int(input("Insert second number: "))

print(f"The average of the numbers {number1} and {number2} is {(number1 + number2) / 2}.")
